Privacy Policy for PlannerToLife
Effective Date: May 7th 2025

Thank you for using PlannerToLife, a mobile application developed by HOLISTERAPIA SRL (“we,” “our,” or “us”).

We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy describes how your data is handled when you use our app.

1. No Data Collection
PlannerToLife is designed with your privacy in mind. We do not collect, store, transmit, or process any personal data or information submitted by users.

All data you enter into the app — including notes, plans, schedules, or any other content — is stored locally on your device. We do not access, upload, share, or analyze any user data.

2. No Internet or Cloud Syncing
PlannerToLife does not use cloud services or remote servers. Your data remains entirely on your device and is not transmitted over the internet in any way.

3. No Third-Party Access
We do not share your information with third parties because no data leaves your device. There are no third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking tools integrated into the app.

4. User Control and Data Security
Since all information is stored locally:

You have complete control over your data.

You are responsible for managing, backing up, or deleting your data.

We recommend using your device’s built-in security features (such as encryption or password protection) to help safeguard your information.

5. Children’s Privacy
PlannerToLife is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. Since we do not collect data, we do not knowingly gather information from anyone, including children.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
Although our app currently does not collect or transmit any data, we may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. Any changes will be posted within the app or on our official website.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data privacy, please contact us:

HOLISTERAPIA SRL
Email: holisterapia@gmail.com

Your privacy matters. PlannerToLife is built to help you manage your life — without compromising your personal data.
